    Our cash and cash  equivalents  at  December  31,  2000 were $97.0  million,
increasing  by $32.7  million  from $64.3  million at December  31,  1999.  This
increase was due to $12.5  million  provided by financing  activities  and $37.1
million  provided  by  operating  activities  offset  by $16.9  million  used in
