    At December 31, 2000, we had $161.0 million in working capital. We currently
have no significant  capital  commitments other than commitments under operating
leases.  We believe that our  available  sources of funds and  anticipated  cash
flows from  operations  will be  adequate  to  finance  current  operations  and
